<div class="bookings-container-show">
  <h1><%= @sizzler.title %></h1>
  <div class="hire-container">
    <p class="price-show">R<%= @sizzler.price%> per hour</p>
    <%= link_to "Hire this Sizzler", new_sizzler_booking_path(@sizzler.id), class: "btn-card-hire" %>
  </div>
    <p class="blurb">
I'm practically a braai whisperer, turning raw ingredients into mouthwatering, perfectly charred delights with the finesse of a culinary magician. My grilling prowess leaves everyone clamoring for seconds, turning every barbecue into a legendary feast that sparks envy among neighboring backyards.</p>
